"While I was busy with the network, I started to wonder how are we different from it, and when we can replace our short-lived brains with this kind of systems. What do you think, will this time come someday? I think it will, very soon, we already don't know what processes occur inside neural networks, there is only an entry signal and the result of its actions, and how it has learned with its own internal rules, wiring up its own neural links inside itself. How is it different from us? Would you like to live in a world where only your mind and your imagination limit your actions? The truth is, I think, living in such a world can be no better than in our own, if there is no goal, and where can goal come from if you're immortal and omnipotent... This time we need an AS VAL. GL Shock stock, ANPEQ-15 tactical device, night scope NSPU-M and a 30-round magazine. Ergonomics above 44 and recoil sum less than 147."